275 Gallon Plastic tank with galvanized frame and skid. There is no wood in the skid. It is all metal. There is a 6 inch opening on the top for filling and a valve at the bottom for draining. This tank was used one time to store Malt. It will need to be rinsed out.

The tank is about 3' 9" tall and base is 3'11" by 3' 4" wide.

These tanks have many uses. Power wash tanks. Watering livestock. Watering remote trees and plants. Mixing bio-diesel. Hauling water to remote hunting camps. Lots of uses. They wash out easy at your local power car wash. The fitting at the bottom is standard 1 1/2" inch threads which you can buy fittings for at your building store or hardware.

I can get as many as you need. Just call me or send me an e-mail.

title: Atomic Izor Ti 7.5 downhill skis185cm
description:
Atomic Izor Ti 7.5 with bindings

Atomic's Izor ti 7:5 Alpine Skis are great skis for people who want a ski they can take from the beginner and intermediate slopes to black diamonds by the end of the season. In the past, you had to choose between easy turn initiation and solid edge hold‚Äînow the compromise is over. Atomic designed the Izor 7:5 skis with a raised perimeter giving them the torsional stiffness they need for hard carves, while leaving the thinness that makes them so easy to turn. They'll crank turns on a dime, which is handy for avoiding little kids on the bunny hill and trees on the glade runs. The Izor 7:5 ski comes with Atomic's Device 310 which is an extremely lightweight and safe binding. .

title: 4 Gallon Rigid Shop Vac Wet/Dry
description:
This is a great little shop vac.  I have had for about a year and it works great.   

Here is the information on the vacuum that Home Depot lists in their website.  

Take on projects confidently with the 4 Gal. Portable Wet Dry Shop Vacuum, this compact 4 Gal. RIDGID wet dry vacuum provides a more customized and efficient cleanup.  The included 4 Gal. RIDGID shop vac is a small, lightweight vac that packs a punch with amped-up power and performance on the inside and a modern look on the outside. This wet dry vacuum has a 5.0 peak horsepower motor that can tackle even the messiest projects. The wet dry vacuum has large rear wheels and casters that provides great mobility over carpeted floors, thresholds, and rough floors at jobsites. This is an ideal vacuum for car cleaning and in-home tasks. Pro Tip: Add a RIDGID filter to a RIDGID shop vac to maintain the power of the vac and extend vacuum life. Add a RIDGID dust bag (VF3501; sold separately) to the shop vacuum to help keep the wet dry vacuum drum clean and for quick pickups.

This is an amazingly beautiful clay pot which is handmade by professional artistes from the rural villages of India and then decorated by their nimble hands and the whole process takes two full days from start to finish. These types of handmade items are only available at the Handicrafts Expo and Exhibition presented by the Government Of India and are sold for export only from India to certain nations across the world including the USA, UK and Europe. These are rare to come by as they are limited and restricted to the number of artistes available and every single piece is unique in its own respect as each artiste has his or her own signature style just like a Picasso or Mona Lisa. title: Mondo Grass Plants
description:
This grass is great for ground cover or for borders such as walkways. Once established it spreads using rhizomes which means that it grows by sending out runners or underground stems. This isn't the dwarf variety, this is the "normal"  variety which grows at about 6 inchs tall.

I am thinning out and have lots that could use new homes! 

You will get 10 fresh plugs (not pots) for $5.00. PLEASE SEE PICTURES.

Please look at pictures provided and read all information before deciding to purchase.

Home Depot sells this in bulk via mail:
$96.00 (54 pots) @ 1.78 per pot. Each pot contains about 9 plugs of grass. That works out to be about .20 per plug at BULK RATE  for a total of 486 plugs. 

Non- bulk rate this grass is sold by the pot at about 9.00 per pot. Each pot contains about 10 plugs of grass so that is about .90 per plug.

I am charging .50 per plug. If you need large quantities I would recommend purchasing from home depot at bulk rate because I will not sell it at bulk rate prices.

Many people ask how fast this will spread and how much they will need. Please read the information I provided. 

Example:

To determine how many Mondo Grass plugs you need for an area that is 3 feet wide by 12 feet long, you'll need to calculate the total square footage of the area. In this case, it's 3 feet wide by 12 feet long, which equals 36 square feet. . My recommendation is 2-3 plugs planted 6-8 inches apart.

For a conservative estimate, let's assume you plant 2 plugs at 8 inches apart, which is 0.67 feet. So, for 36 square feet, you would need approximately 108 plugs (36 square feet / 0.67 feet x 2 plugs = 108).

title: Salomon Sight 2021 snowboard - 153
description:
Salomon Sight 2021 153 cm snowboard in great used condition. Lovingly maintained and regularly waxed, no core shots, no edge damage, just some minor scuffs to the edge of the top sheet and under the binding plates, like you‚Äôd expect for a used board. Had a full base grind, hand wax, and edges sharpened by Stick Docs in Burbank ($65) near the end of last season. 

*Bindings not included.*

I‚Äôve loved learning on it but I need different specs to progress beyond intermediate so I‚Äôm passing it along.

The Sight is an all-mountain directional twin with a softer flex and lots of pop, and quadratic side cuts for edge hold and easy turn initiation. I‚Äôve ridden this from the bunny slope to the summit, in all kinds of snow conditions from fresh powder to refrozen crust and spring slush and it‚Äôs handled everything beautifully. It has a mixed profile with a forgiving, floaty rocker nose and tail and camber between the bindings to keep it dynamic. It‚Äôs a perfect beginner-intermediate board (with all 5-star reviews on Evo).

The design is really aesthetic with a subtle embossed pattern of mountain peaks. 

The dimensions make it best suited to folks 5‚Äô5‚Äù‚Äì5‚Äô9‚Äù, with boots up to women‚Äôs 9.5/men‚Äôs 7.5, past that you‚Äôll get toe drag.

Tip/tail: 290mm
Waist: 246mm

Originally retailed for $400. More details here: https://www.evo.com/outlet/snowboards/salomon-sight-snowboard-2021

Pick up in West Hollywood, Venmo or cash. 

Willing to deliver in central LA for a small fee.

title: Toshiba Portable Air Conditioner, 10,000 BTU
description:
Toshiba Portable air conditioner, attaches to window, plus into wall. All parts included.

Barely used. Works great, like new! Sells for 449 + tax at Home Depot. 

About This Product

Toshiba 10,000 BTU Portable Air Conditioner Cools 350 Sq. Ft. with Dehumidifier and Remote in White

3-in-1 cools, dehumidifies, and circulates rooms up to 350 sq. ft

The Toshiba Wi-Fi portable air conditioner has the cooling power you need to cool, dehumidify, or circulate air in spaces up to 350 sq. ft. while removing up to 3.5 pints of moisture from the air each hour. Smart functionalities include a smartphone app to control your AC through Wi-Fi from anywhere, at home, or through the cloud. This unit has voice control options with Alexa or Google Assistant devices. You can also use the LCD remote control or the integrated electronic control panel and display. The unit has a sleek and modern design and is light and compact. Easily move this portable air conditioner from room to room with the 4-wheel design. This unit comes with an installation kit for quick and easy installation, and it fits in most vertical or horizontal windows. Intelligent features such as the 24-hour timer, sleep mode, and the automatic vent angle for better air distribution help you to personalize your comfort. You can cool, dehumidify, or circulate the air in the space you need and get peace of mind with a 1-year warranty by Toshiba.

Smart control from anywhere with the Toshiba AC smartphone app for Android and iOS, and get your home cool and comfortable for when you arrive.
Use your voice to command your AC and change settings using Google Assistant or Alexa-enabled devices.
Move the unit anywhere with the 4-wheel design and handles, then easily install it in vertical or horizontal windows from 19.5" to 62" with the included snap-together window kit.
3-in-1 comfort with superior cooling, circulation, and dehumidification settings for rooms up to 350 sq. ft.
Digital control panel with LED thermostat and included easy-to-use LCD remote control.
Evenly distribute cooled air throughout your room with the Louver Auto-Swing feature.
Let the air conditioner work on your schedule with the 24-hour timer. You can also run the AC on auto mode, save energy with the ECO mode, or adjust settings overnight with the intelligent sleep preset
Auto restart function saves your settings in case of a power outage

title: Green Artificial Grass Turf 23.6 x 3.4
description:
Brand new.  Never used.  Multi purpose.  Uses include: lawn replacement, patios, balcony, pet/dog areas, RVs and more. Purchased at Home Depot. See online for details. Go to Home Depot site search this sku - [hidden information] and see below. 

About This Product
TrafficMaster Verde Green turf is a beautiful lush green artificial grass. This is made with green blades and green thatch for a rich deep green color. Verde Green can be used for a variety of applications including grass replacement, patio and deck. The 1.25 in tall pile height and three-dimensional blades provide aesthetic appeal and the appearance of real grass. No Mowing, No Watering, No Spraying just years of enjoyment with family friends and pets. This turf is recommended for residential and commercial applications, is safe for pets and children. It is an excellent choice in both hot and dry climate areas where you can conserve water and in climates that are cold and/or wet for a mud free play area, both providing you with year-round green and turf enjoyment. It is recommended to add 1 lb. - 2 lbs. of infill per square feet.

To buy the Verde 12 ft. Wide x Cut to Length Green Artificial Grass Turf online see 325120540
12 ft. wide rolls and you choose the length
Verde green has 2-colors of green blades and green
Blades and thatch are UV stabilized to keep natural grass colors
Uses include: lawn replacement, patios, balcony, pet/dog areas, RVs and more
Recommended for residential and commercial artificial turf applications
Perforated backing for superior drainage
No lead or other heavy metals
Soft, non-abrasive, non-absorbent artificial grass fibers
We recommend always using turf infill in lawn replacement applications for blade support and ballast

TrafficMaster Flooring

Power wash tanks. Watering livestock. Watering remote trees and plants. Mixing bio-diesel. Hauling water to remote hunting camps. Lots of uses. They wash out easy at your local power car wash. description:

My husband can make any size needed, usually in less than a week.  Currently we have a 2 x 2 bin (4 bins total) and a 3 x 3 bin (9 bins total) available.  The storage tubs are from Home Depot and are 27-gallon bins.

The 2 x 2 dimensions are:  44 1/2" wide, 39 3/4" tall, and 29" deep.

description:

Food Grade 275 Gallon Plastic tank with galvanized frame. There is no wood in the skid. It is all Metal or Plastic. There is a 6 inch opening on the top for filling and a valve at the bottom for draining. This tank was used one time to store food ingredients Needs to be rinsed out. The valve on the bottom has standard 1 1/2" male threads. You can go to Home Depot and purchase PVC fitting to reduce it down to whatever size you need. The tank is about 3' 9" tall and base is 3'11" by 3' 4" wide.

These tanks have many uses...

Power wash tanks. Watering livestock. Watering remote trees and plants. Mixing bio-diesel. Hauling water to remote hunting camps. Lots of uses. They wash out easy at your local power car wash. The fitting at the bottom is standard 1 1/2" inch threads which you can buy fittings for at your building store or hardware store. These containers have a lot of different uses.......................Rain collection....Septic tank for hunting cabin...Water tank for a cabin in the woods...Trash cans...Livestock feeders...Collect water from washing machine to watering plants...Drip waterer for chickens...Bio fuel storage...Bio diesel storage...storing or washing waste vegetable oil...Deer Feeder...Drip waterer for plants...Open ended tank for feed storage or other storage...Water Lily planter...Making liquid soap...Camping water source...Caps for sprinkler valves used in nursery's and groves...Water bill too high from municipalities pump rain water through out home...Fill the container with cement and use as an underwater weight for docks...Live well for under your dock...Wind turbine to generate electricity...Live well for bait in boat...Tropical or Salt Water Fish & Pond Filters...Mobile car Wash.

MOISES

title: Montessori House bed
description:
We are moving and have decided to sell our son's bed. Purchased from Home Depot in November 2023. 

We might consider selling the mattress separately for the right price. It is a Nectar Hybrid mattress in Excellent condition purchased in November 2023.

About This Product
Designed in a fun and cute house shape, this bed is sure to add charm and character to your bedroom. You'll love its low height and easy access so you don't have to worry about safety. Made of high quality pine and MDF, the bed is stable and durable. 2-large drawers under the bed provide convenient storage for your everyday items. The simple yet creative look also allows you and your child to decorate this bed together and let their imagination run wild.

Open design allows creative decoration with any special artwork
2-large drawers under the bed offer you convenient storage space for daily necessities
Low bed design does not need to worry about the safety of childr
Made of solid pine and high quality MDF, this bed is stable and durable
All parts, hardware and instruction are shipped straight to your door in one efficiently packed box for simple set-up

Weight capacity: 400 lbs.
Recommend mattress thickness: 8-10 in.
